{
  "stem": "1415.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And if you touched it, you were a goner, and there was-- the space was little.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we-- he gave me in a [NON-ENGLISH], which is a-- like an army-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "An army container.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They're made out of aluminum or whatever, or some kind of metal, which conducts electricity even worse, I think.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And he passed me that along for mother. -- And I-- I took it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I didn't touch any electric wires, because ordinarily, I'm pretty klutzy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And here is the sentry standing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And here I am, taking that across.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I cannot believe that we did that, but we did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We did a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I know I'm making everything very light, and I'm not really going into-- into the heaviness of it, maybe because I was a child, and these are my memories.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And all the bad ones, I want-- I just put behind me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "All-- all the-- the dead bodies that ended up on those wires every single morning, that were cleaned up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Every single morning I-- I stayed in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Or-- or those children that never returned, or our regular tortures every-- every time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I seem to have put behind me, and only remember the incidents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "But I know, as I'm talking, I realize that everything sounds so light and so breezy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "It's like, you're going-- you're going away, and you're telling somebody about your trip.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "But it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "It really wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It really wasn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "I just want people to know that it wasn't a trip.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "That it was real hard to survive every single day [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of my-- of my three and a half years, was a real survival effort, every single day.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
